{
  "id": "RAW_33817b82",
  "title": "刚刚，小云雀的短剧 Agent 上线了，背后是字节自己的 Seedance 2.0。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647680850&idx=1&sn=98cf18fa4224c89c3601cf0cb37c4bb5",
  "date": "2026-03-19 03:29:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就在刚刚，世界第一个用Seedance 2.0做底层模型的AI短剧Agent，正式上线了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它就是，字节家自己的产品，小云雀。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"500197159\" data-ratio=\"0.66\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2400\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=981b0530&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqX2nwC2jdkpoceG4spZibEm4yibwRJegvRdibJdK51NgcrKcHzZ7FOQ1m2Lpzj7BQHKqDfianKICdlzl6IYuKaTI6G8iczpE6Hic4XbQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这一个月为了用Seedance 2.0通宵达旦的朋友肯定都听说过这个名字。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为现在主流几乎就三个用Seedance 2.0的地方，都是字节自己的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">豆包、即梦、小云雀。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">全网现在Seedance 2.0，几乎就是所有AI创作者的最稀缺的资源，几乎都没几家能拿到API的，所以基于Seedance 2.0之上的Agent产品，更是少之又少。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而这次，他们自己把基于Seedance 2.0的AI短剧Agent给掏出来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我是一周前拿到的内测资格，刚体验了一天，我当时就立马跟小云雀的人说，一定要给我个首发。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真的，这玩意，做AI短剧，真的夯爆了，绝对就是生产力级别的提升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">特别是现在AI漫剧如此之火的情况下。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们都知道，Seedance 2.0，现在就是世界第一的AI视频模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是呢，它就是模型，最长只能生成十五秒视频，而且每次生成视频都需要你重新贴参考，重新写提示词。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，小云雀的Agent来了，参考人物，分镜表，剪辑，这些东西，统统都不用了，你只需要给它一个剧本，甚至你可以只给它一个设定让它自己生成剧本，它就能给你全自动跑出来一整集质量贼高的短剧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不是那种流水线级别的垃圾玩意，是真的质量很高的短剧。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">口说无凭，这个Agent直出的短剧是怎么个水平，看一集你们就知道了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我把我很喜欢的一个网文，追了N久，现在还每天催更的《我不是戏神》，改编成了短剧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">下面，就是它的第一集，注意，这是直出，我没有加任何的后期，我连配乐字幕都没加，有一些BUG我刻意没有去改，这就是直接的直出。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">看过戏神的朋友们应该对这段比较亲切了，这就是故事的开头。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">雨夜、大红戏袍的少年、啃饮水机的名场面，还有结尾那个漂亮的悬念钩子，如果他是阿伶，我们昨晚杀的是谁。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7222222222222222\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"4590\" data-height=\"3316\" data-imgfileid=\"500197067\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b46452f9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2F2jjfQoZLoqVJ1ddkMDme5VCHT0pSZoUtO1VzqXH5srjG2OGM4De4V2sPHibbsr0YR29Zjrxcicotvjue5upNz3T1oMUJEpZ0ibnx07KqLvoRrg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是，哪怕你没看过戏神，这集短剧你肯定也是能看得进去的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">整段视频的声画效果，分镜切换，演员的表演，都能把人给拽进去。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">尤其是结尾养父这个镜头，你跟我说这个是AI，exo me？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5527777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2542\" data-height=\"1406\" data-imgfileid=\"500197068\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f976d64c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqVrIBebowKicm4iaoU3vicO9YQccQ7chnYMcia2xT1kibAyrq0P9NnHYdOCdtbbrrgbO1tYb0iaNN6JAUiaFuOibEZ9PXlo2bC0Sy4FvWg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当然了，单论视觉效果，Seedance 2.0也一样强。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但速度就不好说了，也就，一集做个两三天吧。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而我刚刚的第一集，是花了不到一个小时做完的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我还做了第二集。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这一集里，人物一致性保持的也是非常的好。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有第三集。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">让主角换个造型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">当然，会有一些BUG，还有场景一致性的问题，之所以没改，是因为这是我想展现给大家，最真实的小云雀的Agent能力，我没有做任何的后期和调整，这就是一次直出的效果。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">除此之外，我还做了主角陈伶初次觉醒能力的一集，还原了一下我一直在脑补的场面。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">总共四集全做完，也就用了半天的时间。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">半天，一个人，4集，而且是用的Seedance 2.0，直出未改。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">做AI短剧的朋友肯定听的我我在说啥。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真的是，飞一样的感觉，前期的效率直接拉满起飞。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且这玩意儿还不挑风格，啥它都能生成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这是真人武侠风。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">要打斗有打斗，要人情有人情。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且很真，尤其是哥们儿脖子上扎的那根毒针，看得我幻痛了一下。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5564814814814815\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2534\" data-height=\"1411\" data-imgfileid=\"500197066\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8ecd339e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqVKdic2tFVoMH6giajrZDGibxY7OChMicWsiaMYF870rEw1kCudoEQTsmBLZpdJmKNibRoHI1twnImYhlNrlO7XAA2o1vsg4bdaLoF1A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这是19世纪的欧洲风格。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我直接把古早大男主爽文鼻祖《基督山伯爵》搬了上来，生成的效果也是毫不违和，有译制片那味儿了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">除了真人剧之外，用它做AI漫剧，真的也是毫无压力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这是国漫3D风格。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我把鲁智深接济金翠莲父女这场戏还原了出来，每个人物都很生动。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有鲁智深拳打镇关西的这段，我也非常喜欢。鲁智深骂郑屠骂得过瘾，打得也过瘾，拳拳到肉。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">甚至，我还做了一个猫猫版迅哥，还原了他的经典小说《故乡》里的世界。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">怎么说呢，如果我当年上学的时候就能用到这个技术，那我看的名著量大概能提升一倍吧。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我相信，看完这些我亲身跑的case，所有人都清楚，这个以Seedacne 2.0为基地的AI短剧Agent，有多夯了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">小云雀网址在此：<a href=\"https://xyq.jianying.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://xyq.jianying.com</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">点进去之后，首页是这样的，Agent的入口就在下面那个红框框里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.66\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2400\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500197158\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=180e6e54&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqXN2QP4VvnciaJbxadGBtcunJeSo4AYEwX274eiaFqeeqezzL9HlFlfzJLav7ricXmWOTM0iaG6AdwMIIiaJo0p31qUSOqdCXlf84ibY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">点一下，你就进入了这个界面。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.3472222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500197139\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9fd87150&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqX9qXjAwvOEdsHkpFvriaqV3Tqw45icOG1Z0rL5vRYdfE8oUDa0MV2cOoKvyR4yFVpAuqUFFSxAWpCpicMpKZUZxNo95Gf67XZgrc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如上所示，现在Agent支持的输入方式有两种，一种是你直接给它一个完整剧本，它自己去拆。另一种是你跟它口述想要一个什么故事，让它给你从剧本到片子一口气生成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在剧本出来之后，两者的路径是大差不差的，我就先拿AI生成剧本这个比较简单的方式给大家跑一遍流程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">第一步，把你的构思用大白话告诉Agent，就像这样。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.275\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500197140\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=49770495&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqWHFicWIugDnXPIAZ9pRKeXicgFTA6IpDY8iamDmS5EfeGOeqNfJhl0GuaUNYZdWq6HJ5OAnUh9UQGXUYP3j4wxxz5ocumUm7Otwc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，Agent就开始吭哧吭哧地干活了，生成剧本这个过程视难易程度而定，大概要花个三到五分钟。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5339805825242718\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"721\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500197141\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=66072341&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqVRS0icVEH3TpsrCXeibJiaLzTibfC8D5Hx29X0GFJ7TP2ZxkjHuFPDA66Lib8Ty4jjHq9WBy5W5TuLWWAdcG7zrAFCfxdBakmFU1UQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">等了一会儿之后，它给我端出来了这样一个剧本，名字叫，反派男主从书里爬出来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5546296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500197142\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a36c248b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqUBN4UQicjibk0voJWeNnBns9pdKcwgvMq6wTPcGmnZQbGL5mNslhkk6YvicCo6HeianGZjNib5oiaPkRzQEU5IOoBkhEovuHGEPFcTI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有一说一我输入设定的时候脑子里想的是刺杀小说家那样的剧情，不过它给我生成了一个奇幻甜宠剧本，就，也，行吧。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后下一步，选择画风，画幅比例，按你自己需要的来就行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7175925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500197143\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=29a62b69&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqVwuFPBjqVqEtdlK3z1obkT5hiaicc3U3h96ptuVNmjD5FficVYHiaL1gIpgHwjfhCVCKQyvHicoIcVAwRZrkYFuibBVmtZNgAibYYxt8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">再接下来，就是确定人物和场景了，它会自动给你生成人物和场景，这一步大概要花10分钟到20分钟。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5231481481481481\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500197144\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=caf9ceb8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqW8O5daj4xicZ7r0rgPhROqnqfzdicKlYbXWTKPlnvbfJLeNSicQhPHczdzvQEkiad1swndU5KWzlEw6iaQqiaicPO3EvAcThHfDOvPbk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">等到全都生成完了之后，你可以点开每个角色和每个场景，挨个检查，如果需要重新生成，就可以点AI生成，直接改。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7231481481481481\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1675\" data-height=\"1212\" data-imgfileid=\"500197077\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=924f7eea&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqXibaCoD7sq3C6A7aMeg76Pjv0TTSW9I4pSibajjbeel3ox0Yqv6AXHiaahqXq7E8Nrau020E01iargp6g8iamPjbMn62Llp3kT8jrU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">等人物和场景也都完事之后呢，就到分镜脚本了，挨个点击分镜脚本的按钮，它就会一集一集地给你生成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5222222222222223\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500197145\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b3b4ff0d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqWKcdXEFCkxKib6VT0b8RAtCboPHHylpes5SnaMmnh120geK72LBq281g7a2alt1Jfahnh6gKHTHfvkLPDf6vSXkNZYpn1Hw1iac%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">等到一集分镜脚本干完之后，你就可以点进这一集，查看分镜脚本有没有问题，没问题的话，再点击下面每一场的生成按钮，就OK了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5231481481481481\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500197146\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=73b6db0c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqXU62uDy9Mic3cbp25Enn0sbiasWcQ5iapi